snippet.title: Giga Wing - DreamON Preview Trailer
snippet.description:
Video taken from Dream ON Vol.8
Giga Wing - Dreamcast
Developer: Takumi
Publisher: Virgin Interactive

Video Games do not get any more frantic or intense than this. Giga Wing is a full on, non-stop, all action, crazy as hell, shoot-em-up. Players must battle their way through seven incredibly intensive levels packed with hundreds of enemies using thousands of frames of animation. Giga Wing is all about lightning fast reactions and over the top action, just don't blink. It's a pure adrenaline rush
